gur-AwSy qoN ault bwxI (mwieAw) dI Jlk dy swhmxy iQVkw dyx vwlI huMdI hY[
gur-AwSy qoN ault bwxI mnu`K dy mn nUM Awqmk AwnMd dy itkwxy qoN hyTW fygdI hY[
ieh p`kI g`l hY ik gur-AwSy dy ault jwx vwlI bwxI nUM suxn vwilAW dy mn kmzor ho jWdy hn, suxn vwilAW dy mn BI iQVk jWdy hn, qy jo AjyhI bwxI dI pVH pVH ky ivAwiKAw krdy hn, auh BI kmzor mn dy ho jWdy hn[
jy auh bMdy jIB-nwl hrI-nwm BI bolx qW BI jo kuJ auh boldy hn aus nwl auhnW dI fUMGI sWJ nhIN pYNdI,
ikauNik auhnW dy mn nUM mwieAw ny moh r`iKAw hY, auh jo kuJ boldy hn zbwnI zbwnI hI boldy hn[
